                            <comment id="188827" author="doug" created="Fri, 17 Mar 2017 21:15:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have a VM where I have linux-staging checked out and have built 4.10.0-rc7 and installed it. &#160;I then cloned lustre-release and did a pull of your change (as given above). &#160;I then tried to build Lustre with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; sh ./autogen.sh&lt;/p&gt;

