In every kernel version I can find set_task_state() is #define&apos;d in the kernel #Include sched.h  If that is no longer true in 4.10 it&apos;s a whole new issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="188487" author="doug" created="Wed, 15 Mar 2017 17:19:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just tried to build the above patch against the 4.10 kernel. &#160;Get this error right away:&lt;/p&gt;

